      <title>巴菲特的伯克希尔·海瑟薇（Berkshire Hathaway）要求银行支付日元债券交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/buffett-s-berkshire-hathaway-mandates-banks-for-yen-bond-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃伦·巴菲特（Warren Buffett）的伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司（Berkshire Hathaway Inc.）计划在全球市场上出售日元债券，此前亿万富翁透露该公司正在寻求增加日本五个主要贸易公司的所有权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/buffett-s-berkshire-hathaway-mandates-banks-for-yen-bond-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 00:59:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
