    <item>
      <title>与李卡·瑞（Li Ka-Shing）的XI摊牌威胁着中国的亲企业推动力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/xi-showdown-with-li-ka-shing-threatens-china-s-pro-business-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[习近平总统正在寻求将中国作为稳定的伙伴，以使全球贸易战争激怒的投资者稳定。唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）梦vet以求的航运道上的吐口水正在测试这一推动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/xi-showdown-with-li-ka-shing-threatens-china-s-pro-business-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普迫在眉睫的税款增强避风港时，黄金创下了新的记录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/gold-rises-to-record-as-trade-war-concerns-drive-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[戈尔德（Gold）创下了创纪录的纪录，因为一波波动率使贸易商在总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的预期关税推出之前送往尚未达到港假，这加剧了全球经济正向贸易战的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/gold-rises-to-record-as-trade-war-concerns-drive-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 22:13:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
